Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.02,0:00:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,本想多聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.65,0:01:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,搞僵气氛 或者和别人争吵起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不知不觉 开始不表现自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.56,0:01:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,希望有人了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.86,0:01:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我这个人曾存在过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,只要有人记得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.80,0:01:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来 灵魂就不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.39,0:01:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我是高嶋友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,奈良县出身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,生日是1月11日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,血型A 兴趣是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候经常在大自然里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.14,0:01:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,被误以为是男孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 还有还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,总之就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 若叶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对方知道墙壁变坚固了 所以着急了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好 一个人打倒三只就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不要大意 上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不用留后手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,降临吧 大天狗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,全力全开 来吧 酒吞童子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,休想通过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,拳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怪物们 这里就是你们的葬身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这点程度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,对我四国勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者 拳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,涌出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,数量好多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么能输
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,吃我这招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者踢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,太巨大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会 不顾我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:07:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会让你去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,身体 动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,动起来 动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,已经 够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,说是要背负什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,却没能守护
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,像傻瓜一样 勇者什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,只有疼痛 只有受苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,差点被带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,给我动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不要被杀手锏吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,心火灭却
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们人类很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,胆小 脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 容易落入恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我为什么战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.64,0:10:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是人类！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我是高嶋友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜欢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,千回
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者拳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,若叶 你那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了 现在不要说话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真不愧是若叶 成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要再有人走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要扔下我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,千景死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,球子 杏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,明明有人愿意为我哭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,希望有人了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我这个人曾存在过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,只要有人记得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来 灵魂就不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我是乃木若叶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,香川县出身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,生日是6月20日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,血型A
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,兴趣是锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢的食物是乌冬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:14:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,记住我 了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是此时此刻 在这个时代战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那是那一代的最终战了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,只有若叶活下来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,之后为了让天神平息怒火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,探讨实行了奉火祭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,献上了巫女们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,当代勇者没有出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,记录就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,奉火祭…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就是争取时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,整整300年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是园子的先祖大人保护
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就出生不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:14:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,守护世界就是指这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,被托付了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,托付给下一代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,还是结束掉 都取决于勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说得这么不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 我们这一代的战斗已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,希望已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,锄头？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎是很重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是锄头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,锄头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,锄头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,锄头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是秘密武器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 友友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,园子的御记有很多没法读了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我的肯定也会被涂掉很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可是必须要写
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要努力给未来的勇者派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是我啊 你不是认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,高嶋？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们长得一模一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的先祖大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:17:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然似乎不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 这是梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,果然会被这样认为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,说明起来太麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我是高嶋友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你是结城友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,太见外了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我被诅咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然代替东乡很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但天神似乎为此发火了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,发火？ 因为这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一直在做神树大人的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,神很随性很难理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才提到自己是神树大人的一部分？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈应该也读过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我没能活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,当时以为已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但只有灵魂被神树大人守住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你是灵魂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己也不是很清楚 所以这样称呼自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不是鬼魂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不 也算是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不要烦恼 继续说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,当时友奈要是接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定也会变成神树大人的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可是友奈选择了活下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,了不起？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我没时间选择
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,因为太专心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我听到了声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 大家在叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊 勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,关于我今天来的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,由我来承担吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,神很可怕 很随性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但也迷迷糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,迷糊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我和友奈基本是同一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.51,0:19:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,从神的视点看来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈已经足够痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我能代替你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那友奈会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,活在未来的你没必要痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,推给其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,更加痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人痛苦最让我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,痛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,今后能努力下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,努力不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 我只能这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,能和你聊诅咒的事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,来一趟太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要哭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样 已通知结城友奈大人现在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,作为御记留下记录
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,把人类的生存战略 托付给未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这件事 元老院有新的提议
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因为结城友奈大人的神性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.11,0:21:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以成了御姿 才有这一情况
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,结城友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能三百年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,都在等待这样的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,以结城友奈大人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,结束长久以来的神事的时候来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这样人类就会得救
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.86,0:21:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,执行神婚之仪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗任务？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不是墙外调查吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,到底要我们做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,神事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗任务… 我们防人有和神战斗的手段吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:22:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,先前明明没有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,详情事后通知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.66,0:22:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,防人部队在最终作战中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,负责掩护正规勇者们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.53,0:22:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,最终作战？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.22,0:23:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.69,0:23:50.61,Top,,0,0,0,,那个神婚是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.82,0:23:51.61,Top,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1565,27)}什么调查
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.09,0:23:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,塔要倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.61,0:23:53.24,Top,,0,0,0,,不要做什么勇者了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.36,0:23:52.32,Top,,0,0,0,,{\pos(322,27)}没法告诉防人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.42,0:23:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,明明都不知道发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.14,0:23:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是完成型勇者 三好夏凛！
